            <h1>FDA Urged to Make Oysters Safe</h1>
            <p>Contaminated oysters are mainly harvested from the Gulf Coast region, especially during warmer summer months. CSPI urged FDA to set a performance standard for the shellfish industry to reduce health risks.</p>
